MissingVarIsNotNullValue
/ The bright-line guard: a *missing* variable / NotFound / uninitialised read is
/ a null `data` reference (IsInitialized = false, no box) — NOT null.@this. A
/ present null *value* (Data.Null() carrying the singleton) is a different
/ axis. "variable not set" must not silently become "variable is null".
- throw "not implemented"
